# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# GNU Autotools generated outputs — regenerate with: ./bootstrap && ./configure
# Baseline: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/github/gitignore/main/Autotools.gitignore
# Canonical source-of-truth files kept in git: configure.ac, Makefile.am,
# bootstrap, m4/*.m4 (custom macros only — m4/.gitkeep preserves the dir).
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

